targets.expr: sum (increase(span_metrics_calls_total{service_name=~"$service_name", service_version=~"$service_version", service_namespace=~"$service_namespace", status_code="STATUS_CODE_ERROR",span_kind="$span_kind",span_name=~"$span_name"}[$__interval]) or on(service_version) vector(0))

sum by(span_name) (increase(span_metrics_calls_total{service_name=~"$service_name", service_version=~"$service_version", service_namespace=~"$service_namespace", status_code="STATUS_CODE_ERROR",span_kind="$span_kind",span_name=~"$span_name"}[$__interval]) or on(span_name) vector(0))

histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(span_metrics_duration_seconds_bucket{service_name=~"$service_name", service_version=~"$service_version", service_namespace=~"$service_namespace",span_kind="$span_kind",span_name=~"$span_name"}[$__rate_interval]) or on() vector(0)) by (le, span_name))
